    :param grocery: the value string function reomve from the list.
    :type grocery_list: list.
    :type grocery: str.
    :return: grocery_list without the value of grocery.
    :rtype: list."""
    while grocery_list.count(grocery) != 0:
        grocery_list.remove(grocery)
    return grocery_list
    
